v.1.0.2 -> v.1.0.3
- Added a few extra properties
  - Caret
  - Start
  - Intervals

- Caret: currently added only one extra option, more to come in the feautures

- Start: added prop to control when the animation should begin when the component is loaded

- Intervals: added prop to control how long the current word stays on screen after it is fully typed.

- Notes: more to come!